s = input()
print("Yes" if s[2] == s[3] and s[4] == s[5] else "No") 

n = int(input())
a = list(map(int, input().split()))
b = list(map(int, input().split()))
c = list(map(int, input().split()))
ans = 0
for i in range(n):
    ans += b[a[i] - 1]
    if i > 0:
        if a[i] - a[i - 1] == 1:
            ans += c[a[i - 1] - 1]
print(ans)
